Luigi's Second Mansion 2L - A tool for extracting Luigi's Mansion Dark Moon files. Version 1.1
Instructions: Drag and drop a .dict and .data file into the first set of slots, and hit parse. Once extracted, drag and drop file000, file001, and file002 into the second set of slots, and hit extract. It will take a hot moment for bigger files with more models. Everything should be parsed and extracted now!
Credits: * gdkchan - ETC1(A4) decoder from Ohana3DS-Rebirth * A Blob, TrueDread, Manters (all from vg-resource.com) - discovering/posting info about this game. While not much, the info they posted was quite a bit of help to start things off * Twilighter(also from vg-resource.com) - reversing the model format. See https://www.vg-resource.com/thread-32118.html for more info * RoadrunnerWMC - probably the first person to post anything useful about this game's internals, being the nloc python script, which provided me with some clues on how .dict files actually work * CHEMI6DER/TheFearsomeDzeraora(me) - RE, abominable GUI and all file handling code you see in this program(and also grammar mistakes(and typos) and stupid comments all over the said code)
